headline: CME Group (CME): Taking Stock of Valuation During a Quiet Stretch
summary: CME Group (CME) has turned some heads lately, and not because of a major deal or headline-grabbing event. While there is no single catalyst driving the conversation, the stock’s recent movement is enough to spark fresh interest among investors who might be weighing its long-term value. Sometimes, it is these quiet spells that make for the most interesting turning points for a stock like CME Group. Looking over the bigger picture, CME Group’s performance this year has been anything but...
